Human: I need to add pagination to the submissions dashboard. Right now it loads all submissions at once and it's slow when there are 50+ entries.
Assistant: I'll add cursor-based pagination to the submissions endpoint and update the dashboard to load pages on demand.
First, let me update the backend query to support `limit` and `cursor` params:
```
// server/src/controllers/submissions.js
const { cursor, limit = 20 } = req.query;
const query: any = { assessmentId: req.params.assessmentId };
if (cursor) {
    query._id = { $lt: new Types.ObjectId(cursor) };
}
```
